# Attached reference inputs

- `EA1141_v02_20260519.tcia` is a TCIA/NBIA download manifest containing Series Instance UIDs. Use the NBIA Data Retriever to download the actual DICOM files before running the importer.
- `CFB-GBM_treatment_data_v02_20260129.tsv` is tabular treatment metadata. It may be copied into an image set's `metadata/` folder, but it is not an image series.

Example after the downloaded images are available:

```powershell
python -m pip install -r tools/image_library/requirements.txt

.\tools\image_library\add_image_set.ps1 `
  -Source "C:\TCIA\EA1141\downloaded-case-folder" `
  -SetId "ea1141-case-001" `
  -Title "EA1141 Case 001" `
  -PatientAlias "EA1141-001" `
  -Site "Breast" `
  -SourceLabel "TCIA EA1141" `
  -SourceMetadata @(
    ".\reference_inputs\EA1141_v02_20260519.tcia",
    ".\reference_inputs\CFB-GBM_treatment_data_v02_20260129.tsv"
  )
```
